data.description: Popular Lafayette Falls! City utilities but in a rural setting! Cozy Ranch home! 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. Southside location near By-pass, restaurants, shopping, library and more! Sidewalks and street lights. Fenced back yard with patio. Circle street with common access to the middle green space. Eat-in kitchen with tile floor, pantry, corner sink and opening to the living room plus all appliances are included! Living room / great room with vaulted ceiling, newer vinyl tile flooring and slider to the patio. Split bedroom floor plan. Master bedroom with walk-in closet and private bath on one end of home and 2 bedrooms and full bath on the other end of the home. All bedrooms have ceiling fans. 1st floor laundry. The basement is ready to be finished . 2 car attached garage with opener, cabinets, shelving and pull down stairs to attic. 2 storage sheds. Hi-efficiency furnace and water heater. Lawn sprinkler system.
